Dragon amulet
The Lizards who live to the north of the Middle Mountains have managed to make an amulet which controls Dragons. This will make them too strong and that means trouble for the humans. The amulet must be taken away from them!
#subobj  1
Go to the Lizards' valley
The Lizards who made the amulet live in a valley to the north of the Middle Mountains. To reach it, you must go along the valleys around the lake.
#subobj  2
Find the coffer
The amulet is in the coffer that is near the observatory east of the Lizards' valley.
#subobj  3
Take the amulet
Take the amulet out of the coffer.